OL,3,CWoman warns millions are going unpaid
OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,FA woman from Somerset who has
OL,7,Fstruggled to access the benefits
OL,8,Fsystem is warning that an overly
OL,9,Fcomplex application process is leaving
OL,10,Fpeople without vital financial support.
OL,12,FJo Burridge has complex health
OL,13,Fproblems after a bone marrow
OL,14,Ftransplant for leukaemia which saved
OL,15,Fher life.
