OL,3,CWoman warns millions are going unpaid
OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,FThe Highbridge woman now relies on
OL,7,Fbenefits, but believes applying for
OL,8,FPersonal Independence Payments (PIP)
OL,9,Frequired her to fill out the "most
OL,10,Fcomplicated document" she has ever
OL,11,Fseen.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's very hard. It's so
OL,14,Ftaxing, it's emotionally very taxing,
OL,15,Fit's very long and it covers so much
OL,16,Fstuff. I think it's pretty impossible
OL,17,Fto do it in one day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
