OL,3,CWoman warns millions are going unpaid
OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,F"For something that is supposed to
OL,7,Fhelp people, it is almost like, the
OL,8,Fmost complicated form I've ever come
OL,9,Facross," she added.
OL,11,FThe application form is a 36-page
OL,12,Fonline document that asks many
OL,13,Fpersonal questions requiring
OL,14,Fcomplicated and thorough answers.
OL,16,FIt's led one anti-poverty charity to
OL,17,Fcalculate that more than #850m of
OL,18,Fbenefits is not being claimed because
OL,19,Fthose who need it most are struggling
OL,20,Fto access it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
