OL,3,CWoman warns millions are going unpaid
OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,FMichael's charity has spent two years
OL,7,Fdeveloping an online tool to help make
OL,8,Fit easier for potential claimants to
OL,9,Fsuccessfully apply for PIP, and Jo has
OL,10,Fbeen recommending it as well.
OL,12,FShe said: "You can save your work as
OL,13,Fyou go, and get advice on what's a
OL,14,Flikely scenario is going to be for
OL,15,Fyou. I have helped other people access
OL,16,Fit and it has been beneficial for
OL,17,Fthem."
