OL,3,CWoman warns millions are going unpaid
OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,7,F(DWP) says it recognises that the
OL,8,Fprocess of applying for benefits and
OL,9,FUniversal Credit (UC) can be
OL,10,Foverbearing.
OL,12,FIt says it's hoping to unveil plans to
OL,13,Freform these in Spring next year
OL,14,Ffollowing a consultation that was
OL,15,Flaunched earlier this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
