OL,4,Cdue to 'emotionally taxing' PIP process
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the DWP said: "We
OL,7,Fare committed to championing the
OL,8,Frights of disabled people so their
OL,9,Fviews and voices are at the heart of
OL,10,Fall we do. As explained by the
OL,11,Fminister in Parliament, we are
OL,12,Fcurrently considering responses to the
OL,13,FPIP consultation."
